			<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="https://jamesthomassnyder.com/2019/09/24/the-price-of-promotion/#comment-7372">
				September 25, 2019 at 08:52</a>			</div><!-- .comment-meta .commentmetadata -->

			<div class="comment-body"><p>Thank you, Nancy, for sharing this post and commenting on it.  Even though this is very much about the State Department, I thought it might resonate with a larger audience.</p>
</div>

			<div class="reply">
				<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='https://jamesthomassnyder.com/2019/09/24/the-price-of-promotion/?replytocom=7372#respond' data-commentid="7372" data-postid="1444" data-belowelement="comment-7372" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to James Thomas Snyder" aria-label='Reply to James Thomas Snyder'>Reply</a>			</div><!-- .reply -->
